{"id": 1595, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x夸克浏览器】你看腻了哪些打着极简旗号的东西？", "description": "现如今，太多不用心的产品都叫极简了吧……（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 7127, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170330183014csM9T7qPWd3xAUev.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-04-05T03:00:49Z", "options": [{"id": 188673, "content": "网页，除了一个大图，想找的功能不知道去哪里找按钮", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 188419, "content": "手机没有任何按钮  绝对极简\n可还是丑", "image": null, "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692015}, {"id": 188420, "content": "没啥 水一水", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994340}, {"id": 193028, "content": "简单的三角函数恒等变换", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981390}, {"id": 190470, "content": "没有用心做的PPT", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130115}, {"id": 188424, "content": "我们都是外星人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994348}, {"id": 188426, "content": "太简以至无法分辨", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931774}, {"id": 188428, "content": "是的不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 987197}, {"id": 188686, "content": "好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984097}, {"id": 188432, "content": "夸克大法好！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994363}, {"id": 188688, "content": "优衣库 everlane", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867262}, {"id": 188433, "content": "太简单搞到连基本功能体验都有点差了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994362}, {"id": 189201, "content": "夸克浏览器特别好用，界面简单漂亮，你们还有谁想打开uc看到一篇篇的uc标题党呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 996874}, {"id": 189713, "content": "好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 992486}, {"id": 188434, "content": "明明是家徒四壁，硬说自己在走极简风", "image": null, "praise_count": 111, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994368}, {"id": 188690, "content": "VC浏览器，时尚简约，谁用谁知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 851270}, {"id": 188435, "content": "简是简了，质量却不好的各种东西，难道不应该是精简？", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984475}, {"id": 188437, "content": "极简的东西真的很容易种草...", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994375}, {"id": 188438, "content": "夸克浏览器不也是UC的……", "image": "img/option/option/201704051224361kU7egfWY6aA3h9Q.jpg", "praise_count": 84, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 633268}, {"id": 188439, "content": "北欧日式，不晓得为什么成了极简的代名词。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986362}, {"id": 188440, "content": "喜欢极简风～", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994378}, {"id": 190233, "content": "手机自带有浏览器，为什么我自己要再下载一个？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953263}, {"id": 188698, "content": "极简我就认命令行", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 984616}, {"id": 188443, "content": "苹果！新MBP！有病！\n4个USB-C接口！极简！有病！\n谁抓他们CEO去治治病！", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937041}, {"id": 188701, "content": "不是几根线条拼起来就叫极简，你那是偷懒。舒适，明白，清晰还是很重要！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 976286}, {"id": 188446, "content": "Iphone的极简导致现在听歌的时候都不能充电", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 869045}, {"id": 188448, "content": "家装...太多性冷淡，太多人家里都一毛一样……", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 451150}, {"id": 188704, "content": "粗糙单调硬充极简，来太高身价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 731374}, {"id": 188961, "content": "很多产品只是没钱请好设计师，随便设计一下，把这种没有设计元素称之为极简主义", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 768619}, {"id": 189985, "content": "没有返回键的系统让我恐惧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986297}, {"id": 188450, "content": "都想靠极简风来展示自己像大牌，意图和明明是国产品牌偏要起个英文名是一样的", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842498}, {"id": 188706, "content": "不想用心，就说极简。\n真当自来水是Antipodes啊。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994279}, {"id": 188451, "content": "比如夸克浏览器。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628049}, {"id": 188452, "content": "极简，让生活更加简单高效。没有赘余。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994391}, {"id": 189988, "content": "现在信息量太大的时代，极简风格才能有重点的了解东西啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 999404}, {"id": 188453, "content": "那个说弹性力学的，深深赞同啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 628049}, {"id": 189733, "content": "。。。。无语了对你们", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998127}, {"id": 188454, "content": "白衬衫 白T ", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949737}, {"id": 188710, "content": "做一件事我用了一百个app", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 351049}, {"id": 188455, "content": "夸克浏览器", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814662}, {"id": 188456, "content": "觉得夸克挺好的阿，注重浏览、搜索，比某些满屏广告新闻段子无聊视频的浏览器好很多。", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 385161}, {"id": 188712, "content": "极简手机系统，但其实我并不是需要那么得极度简洁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 136828}, {"id": 188457, "content": "把所有快捷功能整合到二级菜单，主页一片纯色便成“极简”。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 879221}, {"id": 188458, "content": "什么都没有就叫简约风", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 991136}, {"id": 188459, "content": "你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 994348}, {"id": 189739, "content": "我做的图。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302800}, {"id": 188460, "content": "无印良品", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 986135}, {"id": 188461, "content": "via 嘻嘻", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974748}, {"id": 188717, "content": "更喜欢扁平化的风格，但这两者好像经常被联系在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 903720}, {"id": 189741, "content": "我做的图。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 302800}]}